BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kh%E1%BB%91c-Vi-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-phu-Chi-T%E1%BA%A5n/poem-MtT3Ty8giRzakCI6V8vRQQ">Khốc Vi đại phu Chi Tấn - 哭韋大夫之晉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/M%E1%BB%8B-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-0uVV-57Tf6KrY8Mu-C1btA">Mị Châu - 媚珠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF/author-1olZ3UNbr3C-_4X52NnUtA">Tự Đức hoàng đế</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Th%C3%B4n-%E1%BA%A9m-k%E1%BB%B3-l%C3%A2n-kh%C3%BAc/poem-hUH9-68c77bTlxSmWPW2WQ">Thôn ẩm kỳ lân khúc - 村飲示鄰曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-linh-th%C3%A1o/poem-gQe75uF8zqsigRLcM6QYwA">Tương linh tháo - 湘靈操</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/author-tbuJ74IPkvZZ32WHu1yvJw">Dương Duy Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Kinh-Kha/poem-0oAHuuZQGe04sHT0DFR5bw">Vịnh Kinh Kha - 咏荆軻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
